values:
So, I broke up with my girlfriend a while ago. No hard feelings there. It just wasn't really working out. We still talk.

My brother graduated from high school. I am proud of him. For a while I did not think he was going to make it. He proved me wrong.

I got a sweet job offer. It sounds too good to be true. Hopefully it all works out. 

Other than this, not many things have been going on.

Every day feels like Sunday. 



I hate Sundays.

So, I really don't know about this anymore.

It's been almost 2 weeks since I last saw her.

It's been about a week since we've talked.

What the hell is going on?

I have made numerous attempts to contact her.

NOTHING.

It's very irritating.

My day started off as a great day.

I was in a great mood.

Now I am irritated.

Ok, next time, friends, you should remind me with relationships come drama.

Yes, I have a girlfriend.

Everything is good with her and I.

BUT, her friends obviously don't like me.

What's funny is that I've done nothing to be disliked.

They dislike me because they think I am taking their friend away...WHEN REALLY I HAVE BEEN DITCHING MY OWN FRIENDS TO ONLY HANG OUT WITH THEM BECAUSE THEY DON'T WANT MY GIRLFRIEND TO HANG OUT WITH ANYONE ELSE.

And you know I feel about that?

I think it's wrong.

Despite all of this stupid crap I am happy with this relationship.

So basically I am in a heap of crap. 

I love it. (Sarcasm.)

Yeah.

Like always, I'll keep to myself about it, because I have no one to talk to about it. It definitely has to do with girl, well, one really. I'm not generally worked up like this, but now I am, she's special.

On another note, don't talk to me; don't hang out with me, because I don't care. Oh that's what they say about me, I DON'T CARE. They say, "Zach, you don't care. You don't care about anything." 

WELL, THANKS GUYS!

It's great to know how your friends feel about you.

Oh wait, I obviously don't care about them, so why should they care about me?



Anyway, I am very sore. I am bruised all over my body. It kind of sucks.

I need a job.

I still need to do my taxes.

I have no motivation to do anything right now.

I basically suck at everything.

Here's to learning to deal with it.

Here's to learning to deal with life.

Cheers.

It's been months since I have even considered writing in here.

And it's sad that during that time nothing big has happened, at all.

I still do the same things, everyday.

Oh trust me, it gets old.

Still, I never do a damn thing about it.

Why? 

I don't know.

So, I finally got a job.

I work at Target on Val Vista and Warner.

Awesome.

I start on the 9th.

I work back room so no one can really visit me.

That's ok; at least I don't have to work with stupid ass customers. 

Plus I know EVERYONE that works back room; I grew up with most of them.

I start higher than most people get paid there too, which is a plus.

Tonight was cool. 

I celebrated Eid. 

It's a Muslim holiday. 

We gave and received gifts, ate good food, smoke a little hookah, and had a good time.

I just got home a few minutes ago; I took some new photos that I will upload onto myspace.

I know, I'm a whore.

Oh well, who isn't?

I hope everyone had a good night.

Mortification.

Devastation.

Indisposition.

Exhaustion.

Reclusion.

Inclination.

Addiction.

Conclusion.

The weirdest thing happened to me today.

I was coming home from school, just pulling into the driveway, and some guy comes up talking about Teen Challenge. So, here I am talking to this guy when another guy comes along. It turns out the second guy was Jared, my old best friend's older brother. I have not seen my old best friend, Josh, in over a year. Nor any of his family that I was once extremely close to. I am supposed to see some of them next Monday... This should be different, because people can change a lot over time. I already heard things about Josh that did not please me. Actually I should have known that these things would happen with Josh. Damn, I have known him for about 14 years.

Oh man, I went outside tonight, and it is bee-you-tee-full. It's nice and cool outside.

My favorite time of year is coming up and I have no one to spend it with. I want to do things for holidays. I don't want stupid drunken parties, I want culture. I want tradition.

Anyone who is up for that let me know.
I am in love with this woman: If you know who she is, then you can see why I feel this way.

Who needs friends?

Especially when all everyone cares about is getting drunk or partying all of the time.

Losers.

You're all weak and worthless.

Four days until my birthday, which means four days until I get my new computer.

What are you getting me?

I just realized I don't know who half of the people are on my friends list here.

There are some people I do know, thanks for using your real names as screen names.

Do me a favor, post your name on this entry please.

That way I can atleast know who I am reading about.

Woke up.

Ate a sandwich.

Went to bed.

Woke up.

Ate a sandwhich.

Went to bed.

Woke up.

Ate a sandwich.

Went to bed.

Woke up.

Ate a sandwich.

Went to bed.

Lately I have been feeling different.

I feel relaxed, lazy, tired yet sleepy, numb, cool as a cucumber, etc.

I don't feel like doing anything at all.

My plans consist of lying around doing nothing or lying around doing close to nothing.

Today I woke up at 12:30 p.m. and did nothing for two hours. I then decided it was time for a nap.

I took a nap and woke up around 5:00 p.m. and ever since I have been doing almost nothing.

This is weird for me; I don't usually sleep much at all.

I feel good though.

I am content, but more so than usual.

It's nice to not have a care in the world.

It was raining a few minutes ago, that was nice. I do like the rain.

I hate when you think you know someone and they turn out to be someone completely different than what you think, unless you dislike them then find out they are actually decent.

Oh well, whatever.

I played Super Nintendo, Tetris Attack. I only played for a short time though.

Then I went and laid down.

Yeah, I feel nice.

So, last night was intense.

Jimmy was forced to drive home drunk, he wouldn't let me drive because I was not insured on his vehicle.

Thanks a lot Andrea, for throwing us out... I'm sorry we found your boob pads. But damn, we were only kidding.

Now Jimmy needs a new front end for his Explorer.

Yes, we did hit something, we ran over a stop sign. Luckily we were not seriously injured.

I am a little sore today, but nothing too bad.

And poor Jimmy, he now has a ticket to pay as a result.

So, breast pads + Andrea= Getting kicked out, Getting kicked out + Drunk Jimmy = One dead as hell stop sign.

So, uh, I shaved off my beard.

I am sad.

I am completely hideous.

I miss it very much.

Pictures are up on my myspace, if you care.

Boo, I don't think that I will ever shave again.

Boy, I tell you, people are fucking dumb. I can't believe how stupid my step father is. I am trying to get back into school and all of a sudden the shit hits the fan for some reason.

Someone called me from Collins College today, he wants me to meet with him tomorrow so we can go over a few programs, so he can help figure out my many different applications, and basically help me figure out what's right for me. I told him that I would meet with him, assuming that my parents, who are paying for college, would have no problem with this. Boy, was I ever wrong? 

You see, I have a problem with getting there tomorrow; I have a flat tire on my car that needs to be fixed. So, I called my step father and I told him what was up. He told me that I can't go to the school and apply because he has to see the paper work that I had received from a previous visit. He was interested in tuition fees and all of that jazz (As anyone would be.) . I told him it doesn't matter because even if I did apply I actually have to get accepted and sign up for my courses before he gets billed. Not to mention the school has none of his billing information. 

The reason why I am pissed though is because he starts yelling at me because he knows everything. I wish he'd shut the fuck up and let me talk...for once. 

Come on, I was holding the paperwork in my hands as I spoke to him. Is that not enough?

I shouldn't be bitching, at least I get to go to school...

Well, it's been a while. 

I don't know why I don't update more often...actually yes, I do. It's because I live a bleak life. I could make it more exciting, or I could keep it the way it is. 

I think it's time to beef things up, time to do things with myself, etc. I am going back to school this fall and I am currently looking for a job. I am going to go to school at Collins College. I'll be doing Visual Media/Graphic Design. 

Exciting.

Anyway, I think I am getting out of here now, Jimmy's house awaits.

It's either that or I am going to slay the robots that have been infesting our youths with aids.

So, I haven't updated in for ever. It doesn't matter. No one reads this shit anyway.

My interview with Zia has been moved to Monday. Fun. I get to drive out there again.

I have been bored lately, extremely so.

Not much has been going on.

I have been trying to find a job, laying around, and just hanging out I guess.

Pretty lame if you ask me. 

My live journal sucks.

Want to know why?

I'll tell you.

It's because I don't have any drama.

I'm just that awesome.

While most, if not all of you have to deal with angst and regular teenagers (Disgusting) bullshit, I am just hanging out, have a grand old time.

In your faces.
What the fuck am I doing?

What the hell?

This is a conversation with my friend John, that took place about 2 minutes ago, I have no idea what to think about this.

What does it mean?

It's not like I do anything to pick up girls.

I don't even try.

I'm not trying to sound like I'm hot shit.

I'm not, not at all.

I just don't get it.

My friend, my extremely good friend is getting upset with me, wow.

What do I do?

Lock myself away until I rot?

Well, it has been a while since I used this piece of a shitty mother of a fuck live journal.

You were probably all like, "WHAT'S UP WITH ZACH?! GASP! Could he be dead? Who the fuck knows? He hasn't been on live journal in forever!" 

Or not.

Even if you don't/didn't care I am going to fucking tell you anyway bitches!

Lately I have been working. WORK WORK WORK WORK WORK WORK WORK WORK FUCK!

I'm in a good mood right now, that's probably why I am typing a lot of profane words.

Besides work, I have not been doing much. I had this weekend off, and I did nearly nothing.

Sunday, Sunday, Sunday, who would like to do something? I have that shit off too.

Well, in other news, fuck off.

Not really. Uhm, shit. I got up half way through that statement and forgot what I was typing.

I hate that.

Oh yeah, I bought a few new things, two cds and two new movies. 

CDs: Rotting Christ and Fields of the Nephilim.

DVDs: City Hunter and Citizen Toxie.

Hell yeah. 

I'm out of here.





























Bitches.

It's been a while. I have been working everyday. I work today too, I work everyday this week. GFS owns my life now.

Nothing has really been happening. I was talking about getting a place with my friend John in a few months. I want to see how it goes with work first. It's sad; I already want to start looking for a new job. The quota is hard for me to me.

If I do get a place, it'll be fantastic. I think my neighbors will hate us.

I also basically got a new dog yesterday, but I am trying to find him a new home. I saved him from getting put to sleep. He's pretty young, 2 maybe. I'm not sure; I'll have to find out. He's really nice too.

Anyway, duty calls. I have to get ready for work.

Well, I thought about getting back together, but I think it is over for good. For her to say she loves me and then move on so quickly confuses the hell out of me. Obviously she does not care about me. Oh well, I suck at the whole relationship thing anyway. I really do. I now know that I am mean to be alone.

On a lighter note, I finally got a job. I work at gfs. A place where I sit on a cumputer for 6 hours, 5-6 days a week, Monday through Friday , plus 2 Saturdays a month for 8 bucks an hour, and if I do good I get 10 bucks an hour. Plus I get health, dental, optical, and other benifits. Finally I will have some money in my pockets.

Im torn as well, I could sit around waiting for atleast an answer from you. Or I could go on with my life and move on. I gave you till last night, and no reply, I talk to you today, no answer. If the next email I get from you doesnt have an answer Im going to be forced to move on. Im giving alot of time, tomorrow by midnight I need an answer. Im sorry this is kind of abrupt, but its what I have to do to stable my life again. so dont take this as a rude or annoying email, just pay me the same respect as I would do for you. Im leaving for LA the fourth and I have plane tickets for two, I could either take a friend, or someone I love. You choose. 

-Her.



This message was sent to her after she told me she wanted to get back together. I told her I didn't know about getting back together and said I would need some time to think about it. I guess she is in a bit of a rush though. I wish I could explain to her that these things cannot be rushed. Sadly, I don't think she would understand that. It seems all she cares about is her, I'm on her time. I have till midnight tonight, if I don't have an answer by then, then I don't have another chance to get back together with her. How lame, I have to meet deadlines.

I did go over, at five, like we had planned. She was asleep, and I tried to wake her up, but she wouldn't. So, I left her a note saying I was there and that I would talk to her later. I went home and two hours later she IMed me, that's when all of that text took place. I really don't know what the hell happened. She just went off the handle, then I of course, tried to stay calm, and failed. Then she messages me telling me that she is going to get drunk and that she is crying because she is afraid of losing me, which isn't going to happen, or wasn't...now that she's been acting this way for a while I don't know. Anyway, then she starts talking about leaving me. I was so confused, after I told her I wasn't ready to break up and after she cried about losing me, which she wasn't. I do like her, but like I said, she's off the motherfucking handle. I tried to be nice and now I don't know what I am going to do. I'm so not used to haveing a girlfriend. Did I do something wrong?

Sometimes I really hate the internet. I find these little things that bother me, think about them, and then get pissed off. Sometimes I do not even think about them, sometimes they piss me off instantly. I know it's terrible. What can you do?

I didn't see Megan yesterday, not at all. I didn't even talk to her. Basically what she and I already talked about is happening. She says she is scared, scared of losing me. She won't though. She is very busy, she works everyday for eight days, she goes to school at night, and that leaves her very little time to do anything else. She complains that she can only see me three days a week, she is disappointed about that. Three days is enough right? I don't know I do miss her a lot. On February 10 I am going to stay with her for a week. It's going to be fun, and I will actually get to see her. Tonight, I also might go over.

I still need a job, very badly. I really want one. I have applied to several places now, and have gotten no calls back. I also still do not have my cell phone; I need that because some of the jobs I applied have only that number to call. 

Oh well.
